data.title: Blanche Ely High
data.text:
Follow Us on Social Media!

Click here to connect with BEHS via Social Media Platforms. Through these pages you can also access Blanche Ely student group social media accounts. Tiger Pride!

We Are a 'B' Rated School and striving for an 'A'

Congratulations to all of the students and staff of Blanche Ely High School! Blanche Ely earned a ‘B’ from the Florida Department of Education for the 23-24 school year based on student academic performance! Let’s keep it going! Tiger Pride! Click Here for more information.

ORDER YOUR BEHS LETTERMAN JACKET TODAY

Blanche Ely is proud to partner with Jostens to offer Letterman Jackets for purchase for staff, students and alumni. Click the link here to design yours today.

SAC/SAF Meetings for 2024-2025-Click here to access meeting information and link

Join us for SAF/SAC every 4th Tuesday of the month! Click on link above to access all of our SAC/SAF Dates.

BCPS Releases Inaugural Broward Business Directory for 2024-2026

Tuesday, August 20, 2024

Broward County Public Schools (BCPS) is proud to announce the release of its first-ever Broward Business Directory 2024-2026 edition.

BCPS Earns Prestigious Designation as a Cambridge Showcase District

Monday, August 19, 2024

Broward County Public Schools (BCPS) is proud to be named a Cambridge Showcase District by Cambridge International Education.

Broward County School Board and BCPS Superintendent Provide Update on Metal Detectors

Tuesday, August 13, 2024

The School Board and BCPS Superintendent will provide an update on the pass-through metal detectors at District high schools on day two of the new school year, including efforts to ensure a smoother, more efficient process.

BCPS Kicks Off New School Year

Tuesday, August 13, 2024

Broward County Public Schools (BCPS) welcomed nearly 250,000 students back to the classroom on Monday, August 12, 2024, making for an exciting start of the 2024/25 school year.
